<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l3"><expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Albrechte<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>frewdemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vnd Parcʒıfaln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l4"><expan>aıchperg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
