<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_464_r1l5"><expan>Erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> lıeben <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe ſıch eẅr freẅnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l6"><expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>lıechtenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> beklag / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> tecʒel . Darauf Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l7">bıtt / von <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l8"><expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Peter tecʒel für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l9">vns beſandt vnd <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> mıt Jm <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt / Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l10">wıe Jn der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>lıechtenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> / niht hab bey gleıchen pıllıchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l11">dingen <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> beleıben <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd Jn ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dürplıchen</expan> ſcheden da mit bracht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l12">hab . ſo hab er auch vormals bey ſechs <expan>freẅntlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> teg mıt <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l13"><expan>lıechtenſtein<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> geſücht daʒ Jm kein gleıch pıllıch ent der ſache </ab>
