<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l15">gerıchten da ſıch das gepürt hat . arbeyten hab müſſen vnd ſprıcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l16">dıe ſache hab ſıch nu <expan>ſov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> gemacht . daʒ Jm on <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l17">hercʒog <expan>Johannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von Peyern vnd <expan>hint<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> niht füklıch ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l18">keinrley <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> tag oder teydıng ʒu ſuchen / So hat vns auch <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
