<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l20"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / <expan>Deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l21"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / Darinn Jr <expan>eygenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>det</expan> wıe <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſache gehandelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l22">vnd geſtalt ſeyn Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> das von vns ın gut ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_464_r1l23">verſteen . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
